Books APIs

step 1 :

run npm i command to install all the dependencies

step 2 :

use command npm start to start the server (make sure your mongoDB service is running before executing this command)

step 3:

Add books using http://localhost:3000/book/add \*

step 4:

to get books based on genre http://localhost:3000/book/getByGenre?genre= and use query param "genre" to specify the genre name \*

step 5:

to get the avarage rating of the book use http://localhost:3000/book/getAverageRating?title= and use query param "title" to specify the title of the book \*

\*please refer to the postman collection added in the mail to better understand the requests and responses
